race.description: Team Poly Tanks F&M Maiden Plate
race.comment: How much does race fitness count for? SENSATIONAL SECRET (2) is rock-hard fit, having had four runs this preparation. She's placed four from six overall and looks capable of breaking her maiden. From barrier two she will race handy and potentially even lead. Depending on how much pressure she cops, she can give a big kick. SYNTHESISE (12) looks well above average and wasn't far away in Stakes grade as a 2YO. Her jump outs have been solid this time in but she will likely concede a start from the wide barrier. She will be powering home and looks the danger. BRIMARVI ROSEMARIE (1) might be able to settle closer from the low draw. She's been betting back and powering home for placings at her last two starts. Others for exotics might be BOLD STARLET (8) and SHE'S THE RUMOUR (3).
